Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Destruction of I-Consciousness
  - 56
  - 80
By: Abu Sa'id ibn Abi ’I-Khayr
---
He (Abu Sa'td) was asked, ‘What is evil and what is the worst evil?’
He replied, ‘Evil is “thou"; and the worst evil is “thou”, when thou
knowest it not.’
